{"abstract": "Watermarking is crucial for protecting the copyright of AI-generated images. We propose WMAdapter, a diffusion model watermark plugin that takes user-specified watermark information and allows for seamless watermark imprinting during the diffusion generation process. WMAdapter is efficient and robust, with a strong emphasis on high generation quality. To achieve this, we make two key designs: (1) We develop a contextual adapter structure that is lightweight and enables effective knowledge transfer from heavily pretrained post-hoc watermarking models. (2) We introduce an extra finetuning step and design a hybrid finetuning strategy to further improve image quality and eliminate tiny artifacts. Empirical results demonstrate that WMAdapter offers strong flexibility, exceptional image generation quality and competitive watermark robustness.", "referenced_work_ids": ["dd0ebe7c71819a61ac6cc7a2d21665f83d52415d", "e4e8c35c4ef76dcb4598557ab957abc883b80e3b", "240cb6443ed36e6114e20a43652ab595eacc0c4b", "659395d8c131c0898be543f01cd8d2719e760f30", "157be85306dce2536edeb6b89eafd7fffde183ca", "89a7c81e6ca23e3ed74c37c8b9b4fde335f07639", "7ead75362398ef3c2d9f9289d8bc0dbdb6cfd26f", "51ee6e799c1faae57b1736941d9d289fcce72b61", "0642987b05e6f211dff7cde9f57d17fc8e138cdb", "1206b05eae5a06ba662ae79fb291b50e359c4f42", "f4bfb005050828fdd6d2899668b3221e3d962195", "0223d77aa79957097b09fb8d83fc44a61b00d076", "a5b7fc1bff0910ff31975ec0a15ed30c41f0a968", "2854e5bab8e6f36e54c64456628a9559bf67019e", "c1caa303549764d220ff17dc1785985dd1ba6047", "d7890d1906d95c4ae4c430b350455156d6d8aed9", "7962cae10754ac3e9d1836f129febbcb904e4b6c", "de0d20742bb37f866324fb6c1db9736a76ecdbec", "f653569b131176dfed8842694b5ad2ead5e4b923", "9bdb6d5bb94479a8612c41657d55bceef4898f98", "bbaa96aee8b56a85ce005783823f1620700cc851", "6f648aeb5c5219cf021840eaf3df03ac86cebff4", "77fa06b12aea62f13c91d8dc666c7ef2b26662ff", "efbe97d20c4ffe356e8826c01dc550bacc405add", "736973165f98105fec3729b7db414ae4d80fcbeb", "a1495979b7